EZDTP 协议规范
TCP based
第一个字符串规定了模式
[str:Auth]
REQ long:uid
RSP str:password_hash
REQ str:password_salted_sha256
RSP int:status(0:ok|1:pw_error)
status=0?RSP str:access_token
EOT

[str:Token]
REQ str:access_token|int:mode(0:query|1:update_timeout)
RSP int:status(0:ok|1:error)
status=0?RSP long:uid|long:timeout
EOT

[str:Create]
REQ str:access_token|str:room_name|

[str:Connect]
REQ str:access_token|str:room_id
RSP int:status(0:ok|1:token_error|2:room_id_error|3:no_permission)

UDP based
[str:TmpTx]

access token 与 socket 绑定，每次请求不再单独输入